<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>منصة أطياف التعليمية - نظام تسجيل الطلاب المتقدم</title>
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
body {
font-family: 'Tahoma', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
min-height: 100vh;
padding: 20px;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
.container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
.page {
background: white;
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 30px;
box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
margin-bottom: 20px;
transition: transform 0.2s;
}
.page:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
.header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
.cover {
width: 100%;
height: 150px;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
border-radius: 15px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
position: relative;
overflow: hidden;
cursor: pointer;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
color: white;
font-size: 14px;
background-size: cover;
background-position: center;
transition: all 0.3s;
}
.cover:hover { transform: scale(1.01); }
.cover span { background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); padding: 8px 15px; border-radius: 25px; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }
.profile-img {
width: 100px;
height: 100px;
border-radius: 50%;
border: 4px solid white;
background: #e0e0e0;
margin: -50px auto 0;
display: flex;
align-items: center;
justify-content: center;
font-size: 40px;
cursor: pointer;
overflow: hidden;
background-color: white;
box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
position: relative;
z-index: 2;
transition: all 0.3s;
}
.profile-img:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
.profile-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
.platform-name input {
text-align: center;
font-size: 24px;
font-weight: bold;
border: none;
border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
padding: 10px;
width: 100%;
transition: all 0.3s;
}
.platform-name input:focus { border-bottom-color: #764ba2; outline: none; }
.form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
label { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: bold; color: #333; }
input, textarea, select {
width: 100%;
padding: 12px;
border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
border-radius: 10px;
font-size: 16px;
transition: all 0.3s;
}
input:focus, textarea:focus, select:focus { border-color: #667eea; outline: none; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(102,126,234,0.1); }
.phone-group { display: flex; gap: 10px; }
.phone-group select { width: 120px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.phone-group input { flex: 1; }
button {
width: 100%;
padding: 14px;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
color: white;
border: none;
border-radius: 10px;
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: bold;
cursor: pointer;
margin-top: 10px;
transition: all 0.2s;
}
button:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
button:active { transform: translateY(0); }
.btn-back { background: #95a5a6; }
.btn-excel { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60, #2ecc71); }
.btn-home { background: #555; margin-top: 5px; }
.btn-danger { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b); }
.btn-warning { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #e67e22); }
.whatsapp-btn { background: #25d366; color: white; border: none; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 5px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.whatsapp-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: #128C7E; }
.error { background: #fee; color: #c33; padding: 12px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 15px; text-align: center; border-right: 4px solid #c33; }
.success-msg { background: #d4edda; color: #155724; padding: 12px; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 10px; border-right: 4px solid #28a745; }
.hidden { display: none; }
.file-preview { margin-top: 10px; padding: 10px; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; }
.file-preview img { max-width: 100%; max-height: 150px; border-radius: 10px; }
.info-card {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f4ff, #e8edf5);
border-radius: 15px;
padding: 20px;
margin-top: 25px;
border-right: 5px solid #667eea;
}
.info-card h4 { color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea; padding-bottom: 8px; }
.info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed #ccc; }
.info-label { font-weight: bold; color: #555; }
.info-value { color: #333; font-weight: 500; }
.row-2cols { display: flex; gap: 15px; }
.row-2cols .form-group { flex: 1; }
.stage-readonly { background: #f0f0f0; cursor: not-allowed; }
.success-page { text-align: center; background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 60px 30px; }
.success-title { font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.success-message { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #27ae60; margin: 30px 0; }
.success-subtitle { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #667eea; margin-top: 20px; }
.admin-panel {
background: white;
border-radius: 20px;
padding: 20px;
margin-top: 20px;
box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}
.admin-header {
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 10px;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.admin-header h3 { color: #667eea; font-size: 24px; }
.admin-buttons { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.admin-buttons button { width: auto; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 0; }
.student-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; overflow-x: auto; display: block; }
.student-table th, .student-table td { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; text-align: right; }
.student-table th { background: #667eea; color: white; font-weight: bold; position: sticky; top: 0; }
.student-table tr:nth-child(even) { background: #f9f9f9; }
.student-table tr:hover { background: #f0f4ff; }
.delete-btn { background: #e74c3c; color: white; border: none; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; }
.edit-btn { background: #f39c12; color: white; border: none; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; margin-left: 5px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.delete-btn:hover, .edit-btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); }
.stats { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea22, #764ba222); padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold; }
.login-options { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.login-options button { flex: 1; margin-top: 0; }
.forgot-password { text-align: left; margin-top: 10px; }
.forgot-password a { color: #667eea; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline; }
.pro-admin-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, #1a1a2e); color: gold; border: 1px solid gold; margin-top: 15px; }
.admin-search { margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.admin-search input { flex: 1; padding: 10px; }
.admin-search select { width: auto; min-width: 100px; }
.stats-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr)); gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.stat-card {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea22, #764ba222);
padding: 15px;
border-radius: 15px;
text-align: center;
border: 1px solid #667eea44;
transition: all 0.3s;
cursor: pointer;
}
.stat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
.stat-card h4 { font-size: 14px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.stat-card .number { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #667eea; }
.profile-thumb { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; }
.old-file-section { background: #f0f4ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; border-right: 4px solid #667eea; }
.download-link {
display: inline-block;
background: #27ae60;
color: white;
padding: 8px 15px;
border-radius: 25px;
text-decoration: none;
margin-top: 10px;
font-size: 14px;
transition: all 0.2s;
}
.download-link:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
.appearance-section { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
.appearance-section h4 { color: #667eea; margin-bottom: 15px; }
.appearance-controls { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; }
.appearance-control { flex: 1; min-width: 200px; }
.appearance-control label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
.appearance-control input[type="color"] { width: 100%; height: 40px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; cursor: pointer; }
.appearance-control input[type="file"] { width: 100%; padding: 8px; }
.small-btn { margin-top: 5px; background: #95a5a6; color: white; padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 12px; width: auto; }
.fields-list-container { background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px; max-height: 400px; overflow-y: auto; }
.field-item {
background: #f8f9fa;
padding: 10px;
margin: 8px 0;
border-radius: 10px;
display: flex;
justify-content: space-between;
align-items: center;
flex-wrap: wrap;
gap: 10px;
}
.field-actions button { margin: 0 3px; padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 12px; width: auto; }
.sheets-notification {
background: #fff3cd;
border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
color: #856404;
padding: 15px;
border-radius: 10px;
margin: 15px 0;
text-align: right;
direction: rtl;
}
.sheets-notification pre {
background: #f8f9fa;
padding: 10px;
border-radius: 5px;
overflow-x: auto;
font-size: 12px;
margin-top: 10px;
}
.copy-btn {
background: #007bff;
color: white;
border: none;
padding: 5px 10px;
border-radius: 5px;
cursor: pointer;
margin-top: 10px;
width: auto;
}
.backup-section {
background: #e8f5e9;
border: 1px solid #a5d6a7;
border-radius: 15px;
padding: 15px;
margin: 15px 0;
}
.backup-section h5 { color: #2e7d32; margin-bottom: 10px; }
.backup-buttons { display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.backup-buttons button { width: auto; padding: 8px 15px; font-size: 14px; margin: 0; }

/* responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    body { padding: 10px; }
    .page { padding: 20px; }
    .row-2cols { flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .admin-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
    .admin-buttons button { width: 100%; }
    .admin-header { flex-direction: column; }
    .student-table th, .student-table td { padding: 6px; font-size: 12px; }
    .profile-img { width: 70px; height: 70px; margin-top: -35px; }
    .cover { height: 100px; }
    .phone-group select { width: 90px; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .field-item { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
    .field-actions { display: flex; justify-content: center; }
}

/* animation */
@keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
.page, .admin-panel { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<div id="choicePage" class="page">
<div class="header">
<div class="cover" id="coverAreaDisplay"><span>🏫 منصة أطياف التعليمية</span></div>
<div class="profile-img" id="profileDisplay">📷</div>
<div class="platform-name"><div style="font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:#667eea;">منصة أطياف التعليمية</div></div>
</div>
<div class="login-options">
<button onclick="showLoginPage()">🔐 تسجيل الدخول</button>
<button onclick="showRegisterPage()">📝 تسجيل جديد</button>
</div>
<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;">
<button onclick="showAdminLogin()" style="background: #555; width: auto; padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 12px;">🔐 دخول المسؤول</button>
<button onclick="showProAdminPanel()" class="pro-admin-btn" style="width: auto; padding: 8px 20px; font-size: 12px;">⚙️ لوحة المسؤول المتقدمة</button>
</div>
</div>

<div id="loginPage" class="page hidden">
<h2 style="margin-bottom:20px; color:#667eea; text-align:center;">🔐 تسجيل الدخول</h2>
<div class="form-group"><label>الرقم الجامعي *</label><input type="text" id="loginUniversityId" placeholder="أدخل الرقم الجامعي"></div>
<div class="form-group"><label>كلمة السر *</label><input type="password" id="loginPassword" placeholder="أدخل كلمة المرور"></div>
<div class="forgot-password"><a onclick="showForgotPassword()">نسيت كلمة السر؟</a></div>
<button onclick="doLogin()">دخول ✅</button>
<button onclick="backToHome()" class="btn-home">🏠 رجوع للرئيسية</button>
<div id="loginError" class="error hidden"></div>
</div>

<div id="forgotPage" class="page hidden">
<h2 style="margin-bottom:20px; color:#667eea; text-align:center;">🔑 استعادة كلمة السر</h2>
<div class="form-group"><label>الرقم الجامعي *</label><input type="text" id="forgotUniId" placeholder="أدخل الرقم الجامعي"></div>
<div class="form-group"><label>رقم الجوال *</label><input type="tel" id="forgotPhone" placeholder="أدخل رقم الجوال"></div>
<button onclick="sendNewPassword()" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#25d366,#128C7E);">📱 إرسال كلمة سر جديدة للواتساب</button>
<button onclick="backToHome()" class="btn-home">🏠 رجوع للرئيسية</button>
<div id="forgotError" class="error hidden"></div>
<div id="forgotSuccess" class="success-msg hidden"></div>
</div>

<div id="page1" class="page hidden">
<div class="header">
<div class="cover" id="coverArea" onclick="document.getElementById('coverFileInput').click()"><span>🖼️ اضغط لتغيير صورة الغلاف</span></div>
<input type="file" id="coverFileInput" accept="image/*" style="display:none">
<div class="profile-img" id="profileClick">📷</div>
<input type="file" id="profileFileInput" accept="image/*" style="display:none">
<div class="platform-name"><input type="text" id="platformName" placeholder="اسم المنصة التعليمية" value="منصة أطياف التعليمية"></div>
</div>

<div id="customFieldsContainer"></div>

<div class="form-group"><label>الرقم الجامعي *</label><input type="text" id="universityId" placeholder="مثال: S250054965" onkeyup="updateInfoCard()"></div>
<div class="form-group"><label>كلمة السر *</label><input type="password" id="password" placeholder="أدخل كلمة المرور" onkeyup="updateInfoCard()"></div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>رقم الجوال *</label>
<div class="phone-group">
<select id="countryCode" onchange="updateInfoCard()">
<option value="+966" selected>🇸🇦 +966</option><option value="+967">🇾🇪 +967</option>
<option value="+971">🇦🇪 +971</option><option value="+20">🇪🇬 +20</option>
<option value="+962">🇯🇴 +962</option><option value="+964">🇮🇶 +964</option>
<option value="+965">🇰🇼 +965</option><option value="+968">🇴🇲 +968</option>
<option value="+974">🇶🇦 +974</option><option value="+213">🇩🇿 +213</option>
<option value="+212">🇲🇦 +212</option><option value="+216">🇹🇳 +216</option>
</select>
<input type="tel" id="phone" placeholder="رقم الجوال" onkeyup="updateInfoCard()">
</div>
</div>

<div class="form-group">
<label>عدد المواد المسجلة *</label>
<select id="coursesCount" onchange="updateInfoCard()">
<option value="1">1 مادة</option><option value="2">2 مواد</option><option value="3">3 مواد</option>
<option value="4">4 مواد</option><option value="5">5 مواد</option><option value="6">6 مواد</option><option value="7">7 مواد</option>
</select>
</div>

<div id="infoCard" class="info-card hidden">
<h4>📋 معلومات التسجيل</h4>
<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">الاسم الكامل:</span><span class="info-value" id="displayName">-</span></div>
<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">التخصص & عدد المواد:</span><span class="info-value" id="displayMajorCourses">-</span></div>
<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">الرقم الجامعي:</span><span class="info-value" id="displayUniId">-</span></div>
<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">كلمة السر:</span><span class="info-value" id="displayPassword">-</span></div>
<div class="info-row"><span class="info-label">رقم الجوال:</span><span class="info-value" id="displayPhone">-</span></div>
</div>

<button onclick="goToPage2()">التالي 📌</button>
<button onclick="backToHome()" class="btn-home">🏠 رجوع للرئيسية</button>
<div id="error1" class="error hidden"></div>
</div>

<div id="page2" class="page hidden">
<h2 style="margin-bottom:20px; color:#667eea;">📎 رفع المرفقات</h2>
<div class="form-group"><label>رفع ملف أو صورة *</label><input type="file" id="uploadFile" accept=".pdf,.jpg,.jpeg,.png,.gif"><div id="filePreviewArea" class="file-preview hidden"></div></div>
<div class="form-group"><label>ملاحظة أو تعليق</label><textarea id="comment" rows="4" placeholder="اكتب أي ملاحظات إضافية..."></textarea></div>
<button onclick="submitFinalData()">تسليم ✅</button>
<button onclick="backToPage1()" class="btn-back">🔙 رجوع للتسجيل</button>
<button onclick="backToHome()" class="btn-home">🏠 رجوع للرئيسية</button>
<div id="error2" class="error hidden"></div>
</div>

<div id="editPage" class="page hidden">
<h2 style="margin-bottom:20px; color:#667eea; text-align:center;">✏️ تعديل الملف المرفق</h2>
<div id="oldFileSection" class="old-file-section hidden">
<h4>📄 ملفك الحالي</h4>
<div id="oldFilePreview"></div>
<a id="downloadOldFileBtn" class="download-link" target="_blank">⬇️ تحميل الملف القديم</a>
</div>
<div class="form-group"><label>رفع ملف جديد أو صورة</label><input type="file" id="editUploadFile" accept=".pdf,.jpg,.jpeg,.png,.gif"><div id="editPreviewArea" class="file-preview hidden"></div></div>
<button onclick="updateFile()">تحديث الملف ✅</button>
<button onclick="logout()" class="btn-back">🚪 تسجيل خروج</button>
<button onclick="backToHome()" class="btn-home">🏠 رجوع للرئيسية</button>
<div id="editError" class="error hidden"></div>
<div id="editSuccess" class="success-msg hidden"></div>
</div>

<div id="successPage" class="success-page hidden">
<div class="success-title">شكرا لكم</div>
<div class="success-message">تم التسجيل بنجاح</div>
<div class="success-subtitle">نحو المستقبل مع منصة أطياف التعليمية</div>
<button class="success-btn" onclick="resetAndGoHome()">تسجيل طالب جديد ➕</button>
<button onclick="backToHome()" class="btn-home" style="background:#555; margin-top:15px;">🏠 رجوع للرئيسية</button>
</div>

<div id="adminPanel" class="admin-panel hidden">
<div class="admin-header">
<h3>👨‍💼 لوحة تحكم المسؤول</h3>
<div class="admin-buttons">
<button class="btn-excel" onclick="exportToExcel()">📊 تصدير Excel</button>
<button onclick="hideAdminPanel()" style="background:#95a5a6;">🔒 إخفاء</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="stats" id="statsArea">📈 عدد الطلاب المسجلين: 0</div>
<div id="adminData" style="overflow-x: auto;"></div>
</div>

<div id="proAdminPanel" class="admin-panel hidden">
<div class="admin-header">
<h3>⭐ لوحة المسؤول المتقدمة ⭐</h3>
<div class="admin-buttons">
<button class="btn-excel" onclick="exportToExcelPro()">📊 تصدير Excel</button>
<button onclick="showUnsyncedFiles()" style="background: #f39c12;">☁️ رفع الملفات المحلية</button>
<button onclick="showDetailedStatsModal()" style="background: #9b59b6;">📈 إحصائيات متقدمة</button>
<button onclick="hideProAdminPanel()" style="background:#95a5a6;">🔒 إخفاء</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="backup-section">
<h5>💾 النسخ الاحتياطي</h5>
<div class="backup-buttons">
<button onclick="backupData()" style="background:#2ecc71;">📥 عمل نسخة احتياطية</button>
<button onclick="document.getElementById('restoreFileInput').click()" style="background:#e67e22;">📤 استعادة نسخة</button>
<input type="file" id="restoreFileInput" accept=".json" style="display:none" onchange="restoreBackup(this.files[0])">
<button onclick="deleteAllStudents()" class="btn-danger" style="background:#e74c3c;">⚠️ حذف جميع الطلاب</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="stats-grid">
<div class="stat-card" onclick="filterByGender('all')"><h4>👨‍🎓 إجمالي الطلاب</h4><div class="number" id="proTotalStudents">0</div></div>
<div class="stat-card" onclick="filterByGender('male')"><h4>👤 ذكور</h4><div class="number" id="proMaleCount">0</div></div>
<div class="stat-card" onclick="filterByGender('female')"><h4>👩 إناث</h4><div class="number" id="proFemaleCount">0</div></div>
<div class="stat-card" onclick="filterByFile()"><h4>📎 ملفات مرفوعة</h4><div class="number" id="proFilesCount">0</div></div>
</div>

<div class="appearance-section">
<h4>🎨 تخصيص مظهر الموقع</h4>
<div class="appearance-controls">
